attributes.value: Sees guile and cunning as indirect and somewhat worthless
Finds the idea of fair-dealing foolish and cheats when she finds it profitable
Finds those that deny their impulses somewhat stiff
Considers craftsmanship to be relatively worthless
Finds the pursuit of skill mastery off-putting
Finds the very idea of competition obscene
Sees perseverance in the face of adversity as bull-headed and foolish
Treasures leisure time and thinks it is very important in life
Respects commerce
Is very slow to anger
Often feels lustful
Has great trouble mastering fear when confronted by danger
Takes no pleasure in her talents and appearance
Presents herself modestly and frowns on any flashy accoutrements
Always acts with mercy and compassion at the forefront of her considerations
Tends to consider what others think of her
Tends to be a bit stubborn in changing her mind about things
Hates vows, obligations, promises and other binding elements that could restrict her
Can get caught up in internal deliberations when action is necessary
Does not trust others
Prefers to be alone
Lives a fast-paced life
Is given to flights of fancy to the point of distraction
Rarely sick
Poor analytical abilities
A great deal of patience
